content.content: 1. The following Acts are designated Acts for the purposes of subsection 6 (1) of the Act: Land Registration Reform Act Land Titles Act Personal Property Security Act Repair and Storage Liens Act O. Reg. 759/93, s. 1; O. Reg. 13/99, s. 1.
